title: Zia's Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Health conscious cafe. Offers a daily changing wholefoods menu in addition to fresh fruit and vegetable juices, smoothies, fair-trade organic coffee. Try the vegan chocolate hazelnut mousse. Sells pre-made foods in the refrigerated case for quick meals.
